modules.description: Provides asynchronous logging with message formatting, timestamp insertion, and log level filtering. Operates on strings, log levels, and event records. Enables real-time monitoring in networked applications and debugging of concurrent processes.

Provides logging operations for asynchronous workflows, including message formatting, error handling, and result transformation. Works with log levels, formatted messages, and asynchronous deferred values. Handles error recovery by wrapping results and logging detailed error messages with customizable tags and formatting.
